  "voice": {
    "heroHeading": "Connections Guide",
    "heroParagraph": "JFK has multiple terminals, so you may arrive at one terminal and depart from another. Please budget additional travel time as you will need to go through the TSA screening process again. All terminals are connected by AirTrain, which you can take for free between terminals. Be sure to check your airline app or in-terminal monitors for your next gate."
  },
